  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This model has been applied in clinical research settings to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). Submitted under the Minimal profile; structured Context of Use block is not included in this record.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/cpb-hemolysis-mrl2-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cpb-hemolysis-worst-case-identification",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-generic-cpb-cfd-hemolysis-v1",
